<i>Real Housewives of Beverly Hills</i>.

168
00:08:31,788 --> 00:08:33,748
- Astaga.
- Dia berpura-pura membencinya...

169
00:08:33,832 --> 00:08:35,751
Tapi dia mengikuti semuanya
di Twitter.

170
00:08:35,834 --> 00:08:37,503
- Tidak mungkin.
- Sungguh.

171
00:08:39,464 --> 00:08:40,507
Tapi...

172
00:08:41,883 --> 00:08:43,552
Tapi dia tak ingat itu sekarang.

